.modal-header
  h4.modal-title Evaluate {{vm.lecturer.user.last_name}}, {{vm.lecturer.user.first_name}} on {{vm.course.code}} {{vm.session.session}} Session
.modal-body.row
  form(name="vm.form")
    table.table.table-bordered.table-striped
      thead
        th S/N
        th Question
        th Answer
      tbody
        tr
          td 1
          td The Lecturer has been regular and punctual since the commencement of lectures for the semester.
          td
            label.control-label Agree
              input(type='radio' name="q1" ng-model="vm.review.q1" value="Agree" required)
            label.control-label Neutral
              input(type='radio' name="q1" ng-model="vm.review.q1" value="Neutral" required)
            label.control-label Disagree
              input(type='radio' name="q1" ng-model="vm.review.q1" value="Disagree" required)
        tr
          td 2
          td The Lecture materials (notes and study materials) provided by the Lecturer is explicit and self-explanatory.
          td
            label.control-label Agree
              input(type='radio' name="q2" ng-model="vm.review.q2" value="Agree" required)
            label.control-label Neutral
              input(type='radio' name="q2" ng-model="vm.review.q2" value="Neutral" required)
            label.control-label Disagree
              input(type='radio' name="q2" ng-model="vm.review.q2" value="Disagree" required)
        tr
          td 3
          td The use of multimedia and other modes in teaching are adequately embraced by the Lecturer.
          td
            label.control-label Agree
              input(type='radio' name="q3" ng-model="vm.review.q3" value="Agree" required)
            label.control-label Neutral
              input(type='radio' name="q3" ng-model="vm.review.q3" value="Neutral" required)
            label.control-label Disagree
              input(type='radio' name="q3" ng-model="vm.review.q3" value="Disagree" required)
        tr
          td 4
